### Dữ liệu mẫu — kiểm tra đồng bộ Wallet.Balance
### Điền @token sau login. Điền @walletId sau POST ví. Điền @categoryIncomeId, @categoryExpenseId từ GET categories.
### Điền @assetId từ GET assets (hoặc tạo asset trước). Transaction POST/PUT/DELETE cần JWT có role Admin.
###
### Gán Admin (SQL Server, DB Identity — thay UserName):
###   IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM AspNetRoles WHERE NormalizedName = N'ADMIN')
###     INSERT INTO AspNetRoles (Id, Name, NormalizedName, ConcurrencyStamp) VALUES (NEWID(), N'Admin', N'ADMIN', NEWID());
###   INSERT INTO AspNetUserRoles (UserId, RoleId)
###   SELECT u.Id, r.Id FROM AspNetUsers u CROSS JOIN AspNetRoles r
###   WHERE u.NormalizedUserName = N'TESTBALANCE' AND r.NormalizedName = N'ADMIN';

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7186
@token = 
@walletId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@categoryIncomeId = 1
@categoryExpenseId = 2
@assetId = 1
@transactionId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@incomeEventId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### --- Auth ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testbalance",
  "email": "testbalance@example.com",
  "password": "Test@123456"
}

### @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testbalance",
  "password": "Test@123456"
}

### --- Tham chiếu (lấy id thật) ---
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### --- Ví: số dư khởi tạo 1_000_000 (sau các bước dưới có thể đối chiếu) ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ví test balance",
  "balance": 1000000,
  "currency": "VND"
}

### Kiểm tra balance hiện tại
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/{{walletId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### --- Transaction (Admin): Income +500_000 → balance kỳ vọng: 1_500_000 ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/{{walletId}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": {{categoryIncomeId}},
  "amount": 500000,
  "note": "Lương thử nghiệm",
  "assetId": null
}

### --- Transaction (Admin): Expense 200_000 → kỳ vọng: 1_300_000 ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/{{walletId}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": {{categoryExpenseId}},
  "amount": 200000,
  "note": "Chi tiêu test",
  "assetId": null
}

### --- Transaction (Admin): sửa số tiền (ví dụ Expense 200k → 150k) → balance +50_000 ---
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/{{walletId}}/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": {{categoryExpenseId}},
  "amount": 150000,
  "transactionDate": "2026-04-05T10:00:00Z",
  "note": "Điều chỉnh amount",
  "assetId": null
}

### --- Transaction (Admin): xóa → đảo hiệu ứng category đó ---
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/{{walletId}}/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### --- Investment order: Buy 10 @ 1000, fee 50 → trừ 10_050 ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/investment-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletId": "{{walletId}}",
  "assetId": {{assetId}},
  "quantity": 10,
  "price": 1000,
  "fee": 50,
  "orderType": 0
}

### --- Investment order: Sell 4 @ 1200, fee 20 → cộng 4*1200-20 = 4780 ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/investment-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletId": "{{walletId}}",
  "assetId": {{assetId}},
  "quantity": 4,
  "price": 1200,
  "fee": 20,
  "orderType": 1
}

### --- Income event: Dividend (type=0) +25_000 ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/{{walletId}}/income-events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetId": {{assetId}},
  "type": 0,
  "amount": 25000,
  "eventDate": "2026-04-05T00:00:00Z",
  "note": "Cổ tức mẫu"
}

### --- Income event: sửa amount 25k → 40k → balance +15_000 ---
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/{{walletId}}/income-events/{{incomeEventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetId": {{assetId}},
  "type": 0,
  "amount": 40000,
  "eventDate": "2026-04-05T00:00:00Z",
  "note": "Điều chỉnh cổ tức"
}

### --- Income event: soft delete → trừ amount hiện tại ---
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/wallets/{{walletId}}/income-events/{{incomeEventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
